Efficacy and Safety of Immune Checkpoint Inhibitors in Patients with 
Microsatellite Instability-High End-Stage Cancers and Poor Performance Status 
Related to High Disease Burden.

Pietrantonio F(1)(2), Loupakis F(3), Randon G(1), Raimondi A(1), Salati M(4)(5), 
